sec.p:
At the first signal:


–the acquisition of the two-color pyrometer was turned on at a frequency of 1 kHz;

–the acquisition of the IR camera was turned on at a frequency of 50 Hz.

The operating parameters were:


–an initial surface temperature of 220 °C;

–a normal force of 720 N, corresponding to a contact pressure of 0.6 MPa;

–an initial disc rotation speed of 1500 rpm;

–a total moment of inertia around the disc axis of 8 kgm2.
